<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT1">
<l>nāṉmukaṉai nārā yaṇaṉpaṭaittā ṉāṉmukaṉun</l>
<l>tāṉmukamāyc caṅkaraṉait tāṉpaṭaittāṉ yāṉ mukamā</l>
<l>yantāti mēliṭ ṭaṟivittē ṉāḻporuḷai</l>
<l>cintāmaṟ koṇmiṉīr tērntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nārāyaṇa created the four-faced [Brahmā].</l>
<l>And the four-faced [Brahmā] took over and created Śankara.</l>
<l>Taking precedence, I have announced the deep meaning,</l>
<l rend="indent">putting forth an antāti:</l>
<l>You examine [it well] and receive [it] without spilling.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
